$VER: JISConvert 1.02e

@node main "JIS Convert 1.02e"

JISConvert is a conversion utility  to  translate  Japanese  language  text
between  different  formats.   The   purpose  of  this  documentation is to
explain how to install and operate JISConvert  to  it's  fullest potential.
This documentation is written under the  assumption  that  the  reader  has
read and  understands  the  "User's  Guide"  that  came  with  their  Amiga
computer.

===========================================================================

